node.text:
“If I were to be face to face with my 11-year-old self, I would tell him, ‘Wear that turquoise, flamboyant sweatshirt. Be you, and as long as you’re living your life with kindness and you’re expressing yourself in a safe and positive way, then live it up.’”

You are a work of art, Nick (@nickbutlak), and we know your 11-year-old self is as proud of you as we are 🎨 Thanks for sharing your story and for being part of the Sephora family ❤️

Please follow the @trevorproject, the world’s largest suicide prevention and crisis intervention organization for LGBTQ+ young people, to learn more about how to help anyone overcoming a similar struggle.

From our friends at @glowrecipe: Have you tried this viral duo for dewy skin? These two lightweight superstars deeply hydrate and visibly plump skin while working to brighten and keep pores clear and healthy. Here's how they work:
🍉 Watermelon Glow PHA+BHA Pore-Tight Toner gently exfoliates pores with BHA, smooths the look of skin with PHA, and hydrates with cactus water, watermelon extract, and hyaluronic acid. Just pat a generous amount into skin after cleansing
🍉 Watermelon Glow Niacinamide Dew Drops add radiance to skin and deliver an effortless glow instantly and over time while helping to visibly reduce hyperpigmentation thanks to niacinamide, watermelon extract, moringa seed oil, and hyaluronic acid. Use it as your serum step, as a makeup primer, mixed in with your foundation, or on the high points of your face as a skincare highlight

Available at Sephora.

🧽 Use Nomad's Cream Purifying Cleanser for a thorough cleanse. Its key ingredient is konnyaku, a Japanese root crop used in detoxification. It gently exfoliates to lift impurities while leaving skin plump and hydrated. Rinse well and pat skin dry. 

☁️ There's a name for plumped-up, velvety-smooth skin: “mochi skin,” a reference to the soft, plump Japanese confectionery. To create skin like mochi, hydrate clean skin with Mochi Mochi Luminous Cream, massaging in upward circular motions for soft, glowing skin. 

Available exclusively at Sephora.
